### Hadith 3:320

*Narrated Ibn 'Umar:*

The Prophet said, "The buyer and the seller have the option to cancel or
confirm the bargain before they separate from each other or if the sale
is optional." Nafi said, "Ibn 'Umar used to separate quickly from the
seller if he had bought a thing which he liked."

